Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:34.55,Title,,0,0,0,,Together Forever!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I think about Otani's exam tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...the more worried I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I should send him a message of encouragement...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:42.29,Superscript,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yo, this is for real. You got mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:46.23,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Otani Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:46.23,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Help me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I called around, but no one else could help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure. Just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that's your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Otani-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I just have one question...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it's not about height.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with someone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your insults elsewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? We have a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I was just explaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, oh dear, oh dear. My, my, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey? There's no need to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. He was right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, n-n-nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, uh... Koizumi's... I mean... Ri-Ri-Risa's boyfriend, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? I haven't prepared anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Height—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.12,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm only just over 156 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with someone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:52.96,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Don't refer to me as "this."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Sorry to impose on you like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...asking to stay over so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.60,0:03:01.30,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Uh, let me explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any ulterior motive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, he has an exam tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...but everyone in his family has come down with influenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't what you think. Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My, that is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, but where will he sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he could sleep in my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I mean, I'll sleep in a different room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think! I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I seem totally suspicious, don't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing, ending up like this the day before the exam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing stuff like this... like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll greet them properly next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll look like some useless guy who'd blow his exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I explained everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No. That's not good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serious about the strangest things, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't stand for half-heartedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But that aside, you should worry about your exam for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll want to study all night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go hang out in my brother's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm with you, I'll just end up talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's an emergency, just call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's Otani, he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he was chased out of his home the day before his exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.50,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Do your best\NOtani {make sure this matches previous instance}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...even if he had to meet my parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Would you like something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I wake him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he sleeps for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyelashes are pretty long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani! Wake up, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is your exam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,9:20 am...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's already past 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How long does it take to get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take the train it takes about an hour.\NIf I rush now I can still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stuff! Your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you wake me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,On TV they said that the trains and buses aren't running.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What should you do, Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My life has been a mess since I was chased out of my house last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That certainly was a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much of it, too...\NThat's how unlucky I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you—!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the other exam students are snowed out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's just you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up! Stand up, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got the time for this, then why not run there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Takato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But the trains aren't running...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take the subway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This... This is too mu—!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll apologize if you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't jinx me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've worked so hard, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter whether you pass or fail, as long as you do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste all of your effort up until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't ride tandem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! The subway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.99,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Entrance Examination Center
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, once today is over, I'll say "Thanks for all your hard work" with a smile.
