Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:07:58.90,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Five
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:07:59.07,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:07:59.23,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Five... 5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:07:59.40,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Five... 5 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:07:59.57,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Five... 5 minutes before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:00.23,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Five... 5 minutes before. Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:04.00,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Five... 5 minutes before. Exactly.
