Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:01.17,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:01.43,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:01.70,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I... I've
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:01.97,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I... I've lost
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:02.24,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I... I've lost all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:02.50,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I... I've lost all memories
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:02.77,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I... I've lost all memories of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:02.94,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I... I've lost all memories of my
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:03.30,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I... I've lost all memories of my youth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.00,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: I... I've lost all memories of my youth.
