Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:04.77,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:05.14,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Okay, see
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:05.44,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Okay, see you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:05.57,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Okay, see you later
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:06.37,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Risa: Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:05.91,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:06.07,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:06.37,Typewriter,,0,0,0,,Otani: Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was too loud, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, so you'll definitely be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.70,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Career Guidance Questionnaire
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My future, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Been here long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The results will be out in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, Otani is free from the stress of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't been on a date in ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?\NWhere should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm making it all up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Making what up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't do anything while I was studying,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...so today you can call the shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:08:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got the old bag with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, dressed up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Working?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shoot for a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a supermodel, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing an outdoor shoot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen a photo shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you cold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this okay? You'll get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to start shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You over there, you're being disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! You're amazing, Mimi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A pro... You really are a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these friends of yours, Mimi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The old lady is a total stranger.\NThis is my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, let's use her in place of the amateur model.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who was going to participate couldn't make it. Let's have her fill in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Model?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. She's got the height, and she has nice style, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, no way, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be a model!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absolutely impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, let's go with a girly look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for a really cute look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute? I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason... that person seems really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold! I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wonderful. Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. You look very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I really look cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. Get out of my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's get on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... you over there... could you smile more?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really suited to being a model at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not suited, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I do like watching stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You were really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all thanks to the skills of the stylist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the clothes you pick for me, Nakahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stylist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're flattering me, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels great working with you, Nakahara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I found a job I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you want to become a model?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You were way too stiff in front of the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did think you were cute, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, well... just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become a stylist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A stylist, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a stretch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I do like helping people coordinate clothes and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. Don't worry about whether you're suited to it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just decide that you like it and want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then draw forth your confidence and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Otani-sensei guarantees it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-sensei sure is a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's the question of whether he can actually become a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka! Maity-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We went for a drive, and decided to drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Risa's lover, and this is her man on the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to innocent little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I've just been lied to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been in touch with Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The exam results come out today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, I saw the midget earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,On the bench in front of the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I called out "Hey midget!" but he didn't respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The short boy from the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Risa's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You're so young!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, have you talked to Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.97,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I've been lied to again, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I called him several times, but he didn't pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.14,0:14:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He definitely failed. He is an idiot, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Laughing at other's misfortunes will bring you bad karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd pass first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The number you have dialed cannot be reached at this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please leave a message after the tone, then press the pound sign.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shock!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? How many times do I have to tell you not to scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I need to leave early!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsubara-san, I'll cover for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kohori-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on. Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry! You can dock my pay if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was that age once, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be lied to any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you failed, there's always next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right here with you, even if you need to study all year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani... geez, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Otani! You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's going to die, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the test again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can retake the test next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed. Why do I have to take it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me! I'm telling you, the university accepted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "why"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were looking depressed on the bench in front of the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was so relieved I feel asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't answer your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The battery was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just woke up, and I was going to go over to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What? So you were accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask "What's up with you," you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling asleep, running out of batteries...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how worried I was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I?! You're not supposed to make calls while you're at work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually managed to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...yet you say "No way! Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you got anything else to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi, there's no need to cry like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for you, I wouldn't have tried so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's thanks to you that I passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you really are a worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone decided on their future paths.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, we'll all go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at the very end, I'm still running late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late for your own graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to say the same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to say it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, you idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to rewrite your diplomas as "All Hanshin-Kyojin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't copy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten that you're late?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The valedictorian has come down with anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, it's my pleasure to introduce...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.57,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Geez... Those two idiots still aren't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...our valedictory speech, to be delivered by...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.60,Overlap,,0,0,0,,The ceremony will be over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...to be delivered by Otani Atsushi and Koizumi Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoah, this is long. We have to read the whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. The microphone is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you do it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do half and half.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you read the first half.\NI don't wanna start...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Quiet, quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... These past three years, our teachers have really taken care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to them that we've all grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to grow any taller, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, some of us have remained small.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, here at Maido Academy, we've made a lot of good memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...and had many wonderful experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But today, we say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of us are going far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of us are going to part ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Let's have three cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have the comedy act cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hip-hip...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was able to meet you, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're with me, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:22:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we'll always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
